      "comment_id" : 112019804,
      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "To add the apache package, put <code>dependencies { implementation &#39;org.apache.commons:commons-text:1.7&#39; }</code> in <code>build.gradle (Module app)</code>. If there is already a <code>dependencies</code> block then just insert a new line with this dependency. This is the latest recommended version, as of Feb &#39;20 (see <a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/a/55567755/1541141\">stackoverflow.com/a/55567755/1541141</a>). Then clean and/or sync your project."
    } ],
